flowchart TD

%% User Layer
User[Bank Ops / Back Office UI]
Auth[AWS Cognito / IAM]
API[Amazon API Gateway]

User --> Auth --> API

%% Orchestration
API --> Orchestrator[LangGraph / Step Functions]

%% Async Layer
Orchestrator <--> Queue[Amazon SQS / EventBridge]

%% Document Processing
Orchestrator --> S3[(Amazon S3 - Raw Documents)]
Orchestrator --> Textract[Amazon Textract OCR]
Orchestrator --> Comprehend[Amazon Comprehend]

%% Multi-Agent System
Orchestrator --> Agents[Extraction / Validation / Risk / Decision / Audit Agents]

%% Guardrails
Agents --> Guardrails[Guardrails Layer (PII / Prompt Defense / Output Check)]

%% MCP Layer
Guardrails --> MCP[MCP Server (ECS / Lambda)]

MCP --> Registry[Tool Registry]
MCP --> RBAC[AuthZ (IAM Policies)]
MCP --> Policy[Policy Engine]
MCP --> Validator[Schema Validator]
MCP --> MCPLogs[Audit Logger]

%% LLM Layer
MCP --> LLMGateway[LLM Gateway]
LLMGateway --> Bedrock[Amazon Bedrock (Claude / Titan)]

%% Core Banking Systems
MCP --> Core[Core Banking APIs / SWIFT / Trade Systems]

%% Data Layer
MCP --> RDS[(Amazon RDS - Transactions)]
MCP --> Vector[(Vector DB - OpenSearch / Pinecone)]
MCP --> Ledger[(Immutable Logs - QLDB)]

%% Risk Models
Agents --> Risk[Fraud Detection Models (SageMaker)]

%% Human in Loop
Agents --> HITL[Human Review UI]
HITL --> Orchestrator

%% Monitoring
Agents --> Logs[CloudWatch Logs]
MCPLogs --> Logs
Logs --> Monitor[CloudWatch + X-Ray + CloudTrail]